overview: Sandra has to face a heartbreaking reality. Her mother gets a car accident on the way home to celebrate the 17th  birthday of Sandra. Sandra became an orphan, as his father had already died earlier. More schock happens when Sandra knows from Tante Mia, that she was adopted from an orphanage located in rural areas of Java. Aunt Mia tells about Bu Gendis, chairman of the orphanage, who took care Sandra before adoption.
title: Nyi Roro Kidul Project
